('Tomáš Horák', 3, 'Sound quality is solid but the ear cushions get warm after a couple of hours. Decent for the price.', '2025-12-01 11:05:00', 1),

-- Stainless Steel Water Bottle (productId = 2)
('Elena Vasquez', 5, 'Ice was still floating in my water after a full work day. No leaks in my bag either. Exactly what I wanted.', '2025-10-22 08:30:00', 2),
